106
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:21,020
Crusade against Ghost Valley, restore peace of the martial arts world!

107
00:06:21,020 --> 00:06:27,979
Crusade against Ghost Valley, restore peace of the martial arts world!

108
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:31,720
Supreme Leader Gao,

109
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:36,669
a few days ago at Renyi Hall, you promised

