152
00:09:20,230 --> 00:09:21,709
Hand over the Glazed Armor!

153
00:09:21,710 --> 00:09:23,250
We will all redistribute it!

154
00:09:23,250 --> 00:09:27,090
Yes! Hand over the Glazed Armor! Redistribute it!

155
00:09:27,090 --> 00:09:30,199
