[Disciple of the Twelve Chain Cove]

174
00:10:32,179 --> 00:10:33,080
How vicious!

175
00:10:33,080 --> 00:10:36,640
Feng Xiaofeng! You're full of nonsense!

176
00:10:38,780 --> 00:10:41,439
Feng Xiaofeng, stop spreading your fucking bullshit!

177
00:10:41,440 --> 00:10:44,450
